- Yep.

272
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:15,116
- Okay?
- Yep.

273
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:34,950
- Lyndon.
- Hi, Jack. Come on in.

274
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:36,994
Thank you.

275
00:17:40,840 --> 00:17:44,151
Make sure Symington, Humphrey
