295
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:42,200
Maybe because it isn't.

296
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:44,556
Johnson and his men spent
the last 72 hours...

297
00:18:44,720 --> 00:18:47,110
...trying to convince the entire delegation
you have Addison's disease.

